|               |   SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |     CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |       VirtualExecutionPlan name=sqlite compute_context=memory initial_sql=SELECT `hits`.`SearchPhrase`, count(DISTINCT `hits`.`UserID`) AS `u` FROM `hits` WHERE (`hits`.`SearchPhrase` <> '') GROUP BY `hits`.`SearchPhrase` ORDER BY `u` DESC NULLS FIRST LIMIT 10 |
